      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is ready for a new owner who appreciates a solid runner with some character. Mechanically, the car is functional and reliable for daily use, though it may require some minor maintenance in the near future. The exterior shows its age with some visible paint fading, minor dings, and surface scratches, while the interior is intact but exhibits noticeable wear on the upholstery and carpets. It\u2019s a dependable choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly driver that doesn't need to be showroom perfect.",
