      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable, clean, and runs like a dream. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready for its next adventure. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 34500.0,
