    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 2012 Porsche 911 Carrera is a stunning example of precision engineering, finished in a timeless Basalt Black Metallic that still retains a deep, mirror-like luster. Having been meticulously cared for, the bodywork is straight and true, with only the slightest, age-appropriate stone chips on the front fascia that do not detract from its impressive presence. Inside, the Black leather interior remains supple and inviting; the seats show minimal bolster wear, and the cabin is free of any smoke or pet odors. Every switch, dial, and digital display functions exactly as intended, including the premium Bose sound system and dual-zone climate control. Mechanically, this vehicle is robust. It comes with a comprehensive service history, showing regular oil changes and a recent major service that included new spark plugs and a brake fluid flush. The Michelin Pilot Sport tires have ample tread remaining, and the transmission shifts through gears with the crispness you expect from a world-class sports car. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next enthusiast owner who appreciates a well-maintained machine that balances performance with daily usability.",
